ZH: 请把书放在桌子下面。
EN: Please put the book under the table.

ZH: 这个杯子放在这张桌子下面。
EN: This cup goes under this table.

ZH: 猫躲在床下。
EN: The cat is hiding under the bed.

ZH: 坐在我对面的那个人是我朋友。
EN: The person sitting across from me is my friend.

ZH: 小狗躲在椅子下面。
EN: The puppy is hiding under the chair.

ZH: 树下有一只兔子在吃草。
EN: There is a rabbit eating grass under the tree.

ZH: 请注意脚下的石头。
EN: Please watch out for the rocks under your feet.

ZH: 天空下起了雨。
EN: It started raining under the sky.

ZH: 鸟儿在树下唱歌。
EN: The bird is singing under the tree.

ZH: 孩子们坐在地板上听故事。
EN: The children sit on the floor to listen to stories.

ZH: 蚂蚁在石头下面挖洞。
EN: The ants are digging a hole under the rock.

ZH: 他坐在树下读书。
EN: He is sitting under the tree reading a book.

ZH: 走在街道上不要看手机。
EN: Don't look at your phone while walking on the street.

ZH: 鱼儿在水下游泳。
EN: The fish swim underwater.

ZH: 小伙子坐在沙滩上晒太阳。
EN: The young man is sitting on the beach sunbathing.

ZH: 学生们坐在教室里听老师上课。
EN: The students sit in the classroom listening to the teacher.

ZH: 工人们在地底下挖隧道。
EN: The workers are digging a tunnel underground.

ZH: 他躲在树后面偷看。
EN: He is hiding behind the tree to spy.

ZH: 美国位于北美洲的西北部。
EN: The United States is located in the northwest of North America.

ZH: 孩子们踢足球在操场上。
EN: The children play soccer on the playground.
